| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2063 — Recovery Inhibition (cicada3301)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a05b6ad-7bbe-563f-b9bd-185ddf61001e"
